  <Header />
  
  <main id="main-content">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
        <!-- Article Header -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-6">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Understanding Youth Mental Health Challenges in Urban Communities</h1>
            
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center text-gray-600 mb-2">
                <div class="mr-6 mb-2">
                    <span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Author:</span> 
                    <span>Dr. Sarah Johnson</span>
                </div>
                <div class="mr-6 mb-2">
                    <span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Role:</span> 
                    <span>Youth Mental Health Researcher</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center text-gray-600 mb-2">
                <div class="text-gray-500 mb-2 mr-6">
                    <span class="font-semibold">Published:</span> June 15, 2023
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-wrap text-center gap-2 mb-2">
                    <span class="px-4 rounded-full bg-white border border-primary text-primary font-medium active">Academic Article</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4 mb-6">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Abstract</h3>
                <p>This article examines the unique mental health challenges faced by youth in urban communities, with a focus on access disparities, environmental stressors, and community-based intervention strategies. Drawing from recent studies and community engagement initiatives, we highlight the importance of culturally responsive approaches to youth mental health support.</p>
                <p>Our findings suggest that integrated support systems involving schools, community centers, and healthcare providers offer the most promising outcomes for addressing the complex mental health needs of urban youth populations.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
